0with%20seemingly%20more%20convenience%20and%20lower%20cost%2C%20in%20practice%2C%20many%20of%20these%20self-prepared%20returns%20end%20up%20costing%20taxpayers%20more%20time%20and%20money%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere's%20the%20problem%3A%20Many%20of%20these%20self-preparing%20tax%20systems%20allow%20taxpayers%20to%20view%20their%20refund%20or%20liability%20as%20the%20taxpayer%20continues%20to%20enter%20in%20their%20information.%20That%20can%20influence%20the%20way%20taxpayers%20report%20their%20tax%20information%20and%20ultimately%20make%20some%20inaccurate%20decisions%20in%20reporting%20their%20tax%20information.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0f52f1c-7132-46ab-a847-0339b11c40f0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETax%20software%20creates%20a%20temptation%20to%20submit%20incorrect%20information%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPreparing%20your%20own%20tax%20returns%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%20sounds%20both%20empowering%20and%20economical%20to%20an%20ordinary%20taxpayer.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20this%20can%20be%20true%20if%20your%20return%20is%20simple%2C%20you%20have%20a%20basic%20understanding%20of%20the%20tax%20code%2C%20and%20you%20are%20honest%20and%20confident%20enough%20to%20prepare%20the%20returns%20yourself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20you%20use%20tax%20software%2C%20you%20usually%20first%20need%20to%20enter%20in%20your%20personal%20information%2C%20confirm%20your%20filing%20status%2C%20and%20add%20your%20dependents'%20information.%20Those%20details%20are%20all%20required%20for%20filing%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20necessarily%20add%20to%20or%20from%20your%20tax%20refund%20until%20you%20reach%20your%20taxable%20income.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20you%20enter%20just%20one%20source%20of%20income%2C%20your%20tax%20software%20typically%20already%20shows%20your%20calculated%20refund%20or%20tax%20liability%20even%20before%20you%20finish%20entering%20all%20of%20your%20tax%20information.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20some%20tax%20credits%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fwhat-is-earned-income-credit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eearned%20income%20credit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20are%20larger%20if%20you%20make%20less%20money.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20can't%20deny%20that%20seeing%20a%20super%20high%20refund%20can%20be%20very%20exciting%20for%20most%20of%20us.%20To%20get%20all%20of%20that%20money%20back%2C%20you'd%20want%20to%20submit%20the%20return%20as%20is.%20However%2C%20it%20begins%20to%20get%20tricky%20when%20you%20need%20to%20add%20more%20income%20to%20the%20returns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20amending%20hundreds%20of%20self-prepared%20returns%2C%20what%20I've%20seen%20is%20that%20taxpayers%20will%20actually%20go%20ahead%20and%20submit%20the%20return%20with%20whatever%20information%20they%20entered%20that%20got%20them%20the%20highest%20amount%20initially%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20incorrect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESometimes%2C%20they%20may%20assume%20that%20they%20can%20just%20file%20the%20other%20form%20and%20information%20later%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20how%20the%20tax%20code%20works.%20All%20of%20the%20transactions%20that%20happened%20during%20the%20tax%20year%20need%20to%20be%20filed%20on%20the%20tax%20return%20for%20that%20specific%20tax%20year%20by%20the%20appropriate%20tax%20deadline.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20problem%20with%20displaying%20a%20tax%20refund%20or%20liability%20prematurely%20is%20that%20without%20a%20proper%20understanding%20of%20how%20the%20tax%20code%20should%20appropriately%20be%20applied%2C%20taxpayers%20can%20be%20tempted%20to%20incorrectly%20file%20their%20returns%20before%20all%20the%20necessary%20information%20and%20tax%20forms%20have%20been%20entered%20to%20complete%20the%20full%20return.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22355c470c-89a8-43ea-906f-2df65184b24d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20consequences%20of%20overestimating%20refunds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20can%20be%20tempting%20to%20utilize%20self-repairing%20systems%20to%20report%20your%20tax%20information%20in%20a%20way%20that%20results%20in%20a%20higher%20refund%20than%20what%20it%20should%20actually%20be.%20Taxpayers%20should%20be%20very%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20consequences%2C%20which%20can%20become%20very%20costly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20who%20incorrectly%20claim%20tax%20deductions%20and%20credits%20by%20under%20or%20overreporting%20income%20may%20have%20to%20repay%20those%20incorrectly%20claimed%20tax%20benefits%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20interest%20and%20penalties%20if%20assessed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20owners%20that%20self-prepare%20their%20returns%20and%20understate%20income%20or%20overstate%20deductions%20may%20be%20subject%20to%20underpayment%20penalties%20and%20interest%20if%20their%20return%20is%20audited%20and%20these%20tax%20positions%20are%20disallowed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20IRS%20can%20easily%20flag%20the%20return%20once%20the%20information%20submitted%20doesn't%20reconcile%20with%20what%20it%20has%20in%20its%20system.%20The%20taxpayer%20may%20be%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20rectify%20the%20return%2C%20asked%20to%20amend%20their%20return%2C%20or%20at%20risk%20for%20a%20tax%20audit.%20These%20are%20all%20very%20costly%2C%20time-consuming%2C%20and%20headache-inducing%20situations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ff5d4d0-8e02-4217-97da-bc62ffa21b74%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20worth%20consulting%20a%20tax%20professional%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20tax%20software%20to%20self-prepare%20is%20very%20appealing%20for%20its%20convenience%20and%20affordability%2C%20but%20I%20encourage%20taxpayers%20to%20think%20twice%20before%20relying%20solely%20on%20it%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20have%20a%20more%20complex%20tax%20profile.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20tax%20professional%2C%20I%20know%20how%20much%20attention%20to%20detail%20is%20required%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20accurately%20reporting%20income%20and%20deductions.%20A%20small%20oversight%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20failing%20to%20properly%20report%20freelance%20income%20or%20failing%20to%20check%20every%20form%20for%20accuracy%20%E2%80%94%20can%20lead%20to%20major%20headaches%20later%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20costly%20mistakes%20this%20tax%20season%2C%20remember%20that%20accuracy%20is%20more%20important%20than%20speed%20and%20upfront%20costs.%20Sometimes%2C%20that%20means%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20work%20with%20a%20professional%20who%20can%20guide%20you%20through%20the%20process%20and%20ensure%20your%20return%20is%20both%20accurate%20and%20complete.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcpa-tax-mistake-thats-easy-make-could-cost-time-money-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744114861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f057d863d72727e1994c8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcpa-tax-mistake-thats-easy-make-could-cost-time-money-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tax%20software%20offers%20affordable%2C%20fast%20tax%20filing%2C%20but%20it's%20easy%20to%20misuse%20it%20and%20end%20up%20making%20costly%20errors%20on%20your%20taxes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sheneya%20Wilson%2C%20CPA)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcpa-tax-mistake-thats-easy-make-could-cost-time-money-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Sudan%20to%20accept%20man%20deported%20from%20US%20in%20bid%20to%