3Db_MGyd8TKdQ%26t%3D1s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20creator%20and%20social%20media%20coach%20Brock%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReach%20was%20a%20recurring%20theme%20in%20Johnson's%20interview%20with%20Mosseri%2C%20during%20which%20the%20Instagram%20exec%20dispelled%20rumors%20about%20the%20algorithm%2C%20hashtags%2C%20and%20shadowbanning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMosseri%20also%20listed%20out%20three%20priorities%20that%20Instagram%20is%20focused%20on%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20creators%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EInstagram%20wants%20to%20reward%20original%20content%20made%20by%20creators.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20platform%20is%20looking%20to%20help%20small%20creators%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20out%26quot%3B%20and%20build%20audiences%20on%20the%20app%2C%20which%20will%20require%20engineering%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20also%20wants%20to%20get%20better%20and%20quicker%20at%20driving%20trends.%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20still%20too%20long%20for%20things%20to%20pop%20on%20Instagram%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosseri%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20Instagram's%20top%20priorities%20for%20creators%2C%20Mosseri%20spelled%20out%20several%20threads%20that%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20what%20Instagram%20will%20be%20building%20going%20forward%20and%20how%20creators%20can%20adapt%20to%20the%20platform's%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20always%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20figure%20out%20something%20that's%20not%20only%20good%20for%20creators%2C%20but%20also%20good%20for%20average%20folk%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosseri%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20anything%20in%20that%20intersection%20would%20also%20need%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bgood%20for%20Instagram.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20three%20key%20takeaways%20from%20the%20podcast%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5f9b583-8d72-44b0-b531-8cd04ea43724%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Instagram's%20main%20feed%20is%20the%20'most%20important%20place%20for%20creators%20to%20post'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMosseri%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%20that%20only%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20non-creator%20users%20post%20to%20the%20feed%20on%20any%20given%20day%2C%20making%20creators%20the%20bulk%20of%20content%20in%20Instagram's%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20most%20important%20place%20for%20creators%20to%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20will%20reach%20more%20people%20by%20posting%20to%20the%20feed%20than%20to%20stories%2C%20which%20are%20primarily%20for%20interacting%20with%20friends%20(much%20like%20DMs).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb1fc921-0131-4aa4-baa4-5779ec6ca325%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20DMs%20are%20a%20crucial%20spot%20to%20share%20content%20for%20creators%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMosseri%20has%20spoken%20at%20length%20about%20how%20direct%20messages%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagrams-adam-mosseri-spills-on-podcast-threads-creator-monetization-dms-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDMs)%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20where%20people%20primarily%20share%20photos%20and%20videos%20with%20each%20other%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20released%20over%2020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-releases-many-new-dm-features-chart-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20DM%20features%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20DMs%20are%20not%20just%20a%20space%20to%20interact%20with%20friends.%20They%20also%20help%20Instagram's%20algorithm%20recognize%20what%20content%20is%20being%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShares%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20when%20someone%20sends%20a%20piece%20of%20content%2C%20such%20as%20to%20their%20stories%20or%20DMs%20%E2%80%94%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20metrics%20to%20watch%20for%20creators%20when%20considering%20what%20affects%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20Instagram%20weights%20shares%20to%20DMs%20or%20stories%20more%20than%20the%20other%2C%20Mosseri%20said%20Instagram%20values%20both%20%26quot%3Brelatively%20equally.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20he%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20sharing%20content%20in%20DMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20send%20me%20something%20and%20you're%20like%2C%20'I%20think%20you'd%20be%20really%20interested%20in%20this%2C'%20that%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20meaningful%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosseri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ed1ecc2-6fb1-4ce3-bbc6-2dd485475714%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Instagram%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20SEO%2C%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20app%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20do%20better%20at%20having%20content%20from%20creators%20on%20Instagram%20surface%20in%20search%20results%20for%20Google%20and%20other%20search%20providers%20because%20I%20just%20think%20that's%20a%20win-win%20for%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosseri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Blean%20and%20mean%26quot%3B%20team%20working%20on%20this.%20Instagram%20also%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20do%20on%20its%20own%20search%20functionality%20%E2%80%94%20something%20its%20primary%20competitor%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-tiktok-users-search-for-google-differences-new-survey-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20been%20known%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMosseri%20said%20Instagram's%20in-app%20content%20search%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20very%20good%26quot%3B%20and%20added%20that%20the%20company%20had%20%26quot%3Bstrengthened%20that%20team%20recently%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20roll%20out%20new%20features%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20coming%20overhaul%20will%20be%20Instagram's%20recommended%20search%20button%20that%20appears%20in%20the%20comment%20section%20on%20posts%20(somewhat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreators-tiktok-ai-tool-shows-search-sensational-false-narratives-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimilar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20TikTok).%20Right%20now%2C%20Instagram's%20recommended%20search%20feature%20pulls%20from%20the%20actual%20content%20of%20the%20post%20itself%20(the%20video%2C%20photo%2C%20or%20caption)%2C%20but%20Mosseri%20said%20the%20next%20iteration%20will%20also%20pull%20information%20from%20what%20is%20being%20discussed%20in%20the%20comment%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20where%20the%20real%20interesting%20context%20is%2C%20is%20not%20in%20the%20piece%20that%20someone%20uploaded%2C%20but%20in%20the%20context%20around%20it%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20always%20in%20the%20comments%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosseri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20expect%20to%20see%20more%20of%20these%20recommended%20search%20prompts%20as%20Instagram%20gets%20better%20at%20%26quot%3Bunderstanding%20content%20and%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20not%20every%20post%20may%20have%20it%2C%20Mosseri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-reach-top-priorities-creators-content-dms-adam-mosseri-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744113602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f41eb3a466d2b74ab271d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-reach-top-priorities-creators-content-dms-adam-mosseri-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adam%20Mosseri%20spoke%20on%20a%20podcast%20about%20Instagram's%20priorities%20around%20creators%20and%20how%20reach%20works%20on%20the%20app.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbradley%40insider.com%20(Sydney%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-reach-top-priorities-creators-content-dms-adam-mosseri-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imax%2C%20Toho%20Plot