mpUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Both%20Bangladesh%20And%20India%20Must%20Face%20Some%20Hard%20Facts%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20bilateral%20meeting%20-%20a%20first%20one%20too%20-%20between%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Bangladeshi%20Interim%20Cabinet%20Chief%20Mohammed%20Yunus%2C%20held%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BIMSTEC%20Summit%2C%20grabbed%20more%20eyeballs%20than%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20summit%20itself.%20This%20meeting%20was%20not%20just%20about%20two%20leaders%20of%20the%20region%20using%20an%20opportunity%20to%20discuss%20outstanding%20issues%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20cooling-off%20moment%20for%20the%20two%20neighbours%20whose%20relationship%20status%20would%20read%20%E2%80%98complicated'.%20Evidently%2C%20much%20water%20has%20flown%20between%20the%20two%20states%20in%20the%20past%20eight%20months%2C%20since%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20fled%20Dhaka%20and%20sought%20refuge%20in%20India%20on%20August%205%20last%20year.%20Certainly%2C%20a%20few%20other%20official%20bilateral%20meetings%20have%20taken%20place%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20but%20given%20that%20India%20had%20earlier%20refused%20Yunus's%20requests%20for%20a%20chat%20with%20PM%20Modi%2C%20this%20latest%20one%20in%20Bangkok%20begs%20a%20few%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20the%20meeting%20a%20reconciliation%20of%20sorts%3F%20Or%20was%20it%20about%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20pretence%20of%20having%20normal%20ties%3F%20Or%2C%20did%20some%20larger%20calculations%20necessitate%20the%20photo-op%20opportunity%3F%20The%20change%20in%20Indian%20mood%20is%20curious%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20background%20of%20another%20controversy%20Yunus%20created%20with%20his%20statement.%20Last%20week%2C%20Yunus%20said%20during%20an%20event%20in%20China%20that%20because%20India's%20Northeast%20was%20%26quot%3Blandlocked%26quot%3B%2C%20Bangladesh%20was%20the%20primary%20gateway%20for%20the%20region's%20maritime%20access%20and%20that%20it%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Can%20extension%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy%E2%80%9D.%20Not%20only%20was%20this%20factually%20incorrect%2C%20but%20the%20Bangladeshi%20invitation%20to%20China%20to%20build%20an%20airbase%20in%20Lalmonirhat%20district%20close%20to%20India's%20Siliguri%20corridor%20is%20a%20rather%20contentious%20gesture%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20The%20suggestion%20is%20sure%20to%20have%20raised%20eyebrows%20in%20the%20US%2C%20too%2C%20as%20it%20effectively%20draws%20Bangladesh%20into%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20strategic%20space.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20in%20the%20post-Hasina%20phase%2C%20India's%20limited%20engagement%20and%20the%20US's%20shifting%20priorities%20have%20indeed%20spawned%20the%20risk%20of%20deeper%20Chinese%20engagement%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20India%20Late%20To%20Act%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Yunus%20took%20over%20as%20interim%20head%20on%20August%208%20last%20year%2C%20India%20has%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20changed%20political%20landscape%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20shock%20of%20losing%20its%20best%20partner%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20brought%20forth%20several%20severe%20implications%2C%20as%20the%20subsequent%20few%20months%20revealed.%20While%20India%20ultimately%20acknowledged%20that%20it%20had%20understood%20Hasina%20was%20losing%20popular%20mandate%20in%20her%20fight%20with%20the%20students%2C%20it%20couldn't%20influence%20any%20change%20of%20track%20in%20Dhaka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20controlled%20January%202024%20general%20election%2C%20there%20had%20been%20signals%20galore%20about%20Hasina%20losing%20touch%20with%20the%20ground%20realities%20as%20she%20increasingly%20tightened%20her%20administrative%20grip.%20But%20India%20still%20hoped%20that%20she%20would%20be%20able%20to%20hang%20in%20through%20the%20last%20tethers.%20Ultimately%2C%20however%2C%20a%20Dhaka%20sans%20Hasina%20left%20a%20gaping%20hole%20in%20the%20wall%20for%20India.%20It%20also%20failed%20to%20build%20any%20linkages%20with%20the%20new%20dispensation.%20The%20rule%20of%20the%20mob%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Dhaka%20and%20visible%20domestic%20instability%20provided%20easy%20material%20to%20many%20Indian%20sections%2C%20too%2C%20to%20build%20their%20negative%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus's%20inability%20to%20govern%20his%20country%2C%20given%20the%20law-and-order%20breakdown%2C%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20large-scale%20violence%20unleashed%20on%20the%20country's%20Hindu%20minorities%2C%20provided%20a%20linear%20view%20to%20India%20to%20judge%20the%20new%20dispensation.%20Add%20to%20that%20the%20tirade%20against%20the%20Awami%20League%20in%20Bangladesh%20alongside%20a%20growing%20presence%20of%20religious%20elements%20nationwide%2C%20and%20raging%20war%20cries%20about%20an%20%E2%80%98Islamist%20takeover'%20of%20Bangladesh%20populated%20the%20Indian%20discourse.%20Any%20attempt%20to%20support%20a%20fledgling%20interim%20cabinet%20that%20was%20trying%20to%20stabilise%20a%20rather%20difficult%20and%20volatile%20situation%20ceased%20to%20be%20an%20option.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20Bangladesh%20continued%20to%20be%20seen%20through%20an%20emotive%20lens%20of%20%E2%80%98it-can-only-be-downhill-from-now'.%20Hostile%20cries%20were%20equally%20shrill%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20media%20and%20political%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Anti-India%20Hysteria%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20irritants%20over%20the%20years%20have%20continued%20to%20stress%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20relationship%2C%20despite%20its%20firm%20foundations.%20This%20includes%20a%20water-sharing%20agreement%20over%20the%20Teesta%20river%2C%20border%20action%20against%20civilians%20from%20both%20sides%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20a%20growing%20perception%20in%20Bangladesh%20that%20most%20bilateral%20agreements%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20favoured%20India%20more.%20That%20perception%20was%20rooted%20in%20Hasina's%20style%20of%20politics%2C%20where%20policies%20were%20decided%20without%20any%20public%20debate%20and%20discussion%2C%20given%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20real%20opposition%20from%20the%20parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20added%20to%20the%20anti-India%20hysteria%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20invariably%20led%20to%20youth%20groups%20suggesting%20a%20review%20of%20some%20of%20these%20decisions%2C%20widening%20the%20trust%20deficit%20further.%20The%20Hasina%20government%20had%20grown%20increasingly%20disconnected%20from%20the%20country's%20youth%2C%20and%20Hasina%20herself%20had%20failed%20to%20tackle%20the%20criticism%20coming%20her%20way%20(though%20even%20at%20present%2C%20the%20Bangladesh%20polity%20seems%20to%20be%20showing%20slivers%20of%20similar%20intolerant%20behaviour).%20Dhaka's%20strong%20diplomatic%20overtures%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20also%20added%20to%20misgivings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDhaka's%20Strengthening%20Outreach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20certain%20quarters%20in%20India%20see%20the%20recent%20meeting%20as%20an%20acceptance%20of%20the%20Yunus%20government's%20style%20of%20politics%2C%20the%20meeting%20itself%20is%20unlikely%20to%20change%20the%20course%20of%20the%20present%20state%20of%20bilateral%20ties.%20It%20serves%20a%20different%20purpose%3A%20the%20goal%20is%20not%20to%20embrace%20the%20Yunus%20government%20but%20to%20perhaps%20ensure%20that%20Bangladesh%20does%20not%20turn%20into%20a%20neighbour%20that%20is%20exploited%20by%20hostile%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20extradition%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20from%20India%20will%20remain%20a%20sticky%20point%2C%20given%20the%20complex%20legalities%20involved%20in%20such%20a%20case.%20Both%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20will%20have%20to%20find%20a%20modus%20vivendi%20to%20overcome%20their%20differing%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20Modi-Yunus%20meeting%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20good%20gesture%2C%20and%20nothing%20more.%20The%20bilateral%20frank%20conversations%20were%20a%20useful%20exercise%20as%20India's%20main%20objective%20is%20to%20see%20Bangladesh%20move%20forward%20towards%20inclusive%20multiparty%20elections%20and%20usher%20in%20a%20stable%20democratic%20government.%20But%20it%20will%20be%20a%20long%20haul%20till%20then.%20Political%20witch-hunting%20will%20have%20to%20stop%2C%20while%20various%20political%20stakeholders%20will%20have%20to%20converge%20on%20a%20common%20path%20before%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20can%20be%20held.%20Evidently%2C%20there%20is%20a%20Bangladesh%20beyond%20Hasina%2C%20and%20only%20Indian%20support%2C%20not%20censure%2C%20can%20shape%20stable%20and%20fruitful%20bilateral%20ties%20in%20the%20days%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Professor%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20International%20Affairs%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744113240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Feg307ppg_bangladesh_625x300_08_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fboth-bangladesh-and-india-must-face-some-hard-facts-now-8116455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20a%20Bangladesh%20beyond%20Hasina%2C%20and%20only%20Indian%20support%2C%20not%20censure%2C%20can%20shape%20stable%20and%20fruitful%20bilateral%20ties%20in%20the%20days%20ahead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Roof%20collapse%20at%20Dominican%20Republic%20nightclub%20kills%20at%20least%2013%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744113155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news