%3BMy%20Take%20On%20Parenting%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Thapar%20shared%20her%20thoughts%20after%20watching%20the%20British%20miniseries%20exploring%20mental%20health%20issues%20teens%20experience%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thapar%20claimed%20that%20the%20show's%20depiction%20of%20tense%20parent-child%20relationships%20in%20particular%20touched%20a%20nerve.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20parent%20of%20teens%20(my%20boys%20are%2019%20%26amp%3B%2014)%20this%20show%20stirred%20something%20deep%20in%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20judge%20emphasised%20how%20vulnerable%20children%20are%20and%20how%20they%20often%20look%20up%20to%20their%20parents.%20%26quot%3BKids%20are%20fragile.%20They%20idolise%20their%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20emphasised%20how%20youngsters%20experience%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20pent-up%20negativity%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20feel%20that%20their%20parents%20are%20%26quot%3Bashamed%26quot%3B%20of%20them%20or%20that%20they%20are%20not%20living%20up%20to%20their%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20mixed%20with%20bullying%20at%20school%2C%20Ms%20Thapar%20said%20that%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20one%20of%20two%20things%3A%20%26quot%3Bkid%20taking%20it%20out%20on%20themselves%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20having%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20low%20self-esteem%2C%20and%20self-hatred%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bkid%20taking%20it%20out%20on%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7314108158245842944%3Fcollapsed%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thapar%20reflected%20on%20her%20%26quot%3Bvery%20tomboyish%26quot%3B%20childhood%2C%20remembering%20that%20she%20was%20less%20interested%20in%20traditional%20%26quot%3Bfeminine%26quot%3B%20pursuits%20like%20dancing%2C%20singing%2C%20or%20applying%20nail%20paint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explained%20that%20her%20mother%20was%20worried%20and%20urged%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20singing%20classes%2C%20kathak%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20walk%20with%20a%20book%20on%20her%20head%20to%20seem%20more%20%26quot%3Bfeminine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Ms%20Thapar%20said%20her%20mother%20had%20good%20intentions%2C%20these%20acts%20made%20her%20suffer.%20She%20felt%20that%20her%20father%20was%20also%20%26quot%3Bashamed%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20because%20he%20tried%20to%20transfer%20her%20to%20a%20different%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20good%20intentions%2C%20Ms%20Thapar%20said%20that%20her%20parents'%20behaviour%20caused%20years%20of%20%26quot%3Blow%20self-esteem%20and%20emotional%20eating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recovered%2C%20got%20stronger.%20Not%20everyone%20does..%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thapar%20then%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20character%20of%20Jamie%2C%20whose%20father%20encouraged%20him%20to%20participate%20in%20boxing%20and%20football%20to%20%26quot%3Btoughen%20him%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamie%20assumed%20his%20father%20was%20ashamed%20of%20him%20since%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20live%20up%20to%20these%20expectations.%20Ms%20Thapar%20mentioned%20that%20Jamie's%20father%20%26quot%3Bnever%20communicated%20and%20clarified%20that%20that%20wasn't%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20suggested%20guidelines%20from%20the%20parenting%20book%20'The%20Self-Driven%20Child%2C'%20which%20promotes%20self-reliance%20and%20emotional%20validation%2C%20as%20a%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20underlined%20the%20significance%20of%20separating%20oneself%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20%26quot%3Bfix%26quot%3B%20children%20and%20urged%20parents%20to%20instead%20emphasise%20overexpressing%20their%20pride%20and%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20choose%20to%20bring%20a%20child%20into%20this%20world%2C%20let's%20ensure%20we%20give%20them%20TIME%20...%20Say%20NO%20to%2070-hour%20weeks%20or%20if%20you%20want%20that%20life%2C%20say%20NO%20to%20being%20a%20parent!%26quot%3B%20she%20concluded%20her%20lengthy%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetflix's%20%3Cem%3EAdolescence%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0tells%20the%20tale%20of%2013-year-old%20Jamie%20Miller%2C%20who%20was%20imprisoned%20for%20killing%20a%20classmate.%20The%20family's%20world%20turns%20upside%20down%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20face%20the%20worst%20nightmare%20that%20any%20parent%20could%20imagine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744111140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fs70msglg_namita-thapar_625x300_03_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fnetflixs-adolescence-70-hour-workweek-in-shark-tank-judge-namita-thapars-parenting-tip-8115804%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Entrepreneur%20Namita%20Thapar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20the%2070-hour%20workweek%2C%20has%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%20for%20its%20proponents%3A%20watch%20Adolescence%20on%20Netflix.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Caught%20On%20CCTV%3A%20Late-Night%20Grenade%20Attack%20At%20BJP%20Leader's%20Punjab%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFootage%20from%20CCTV%20cameras%20outside%20and%20inside%20the%20Jalandhar%20home%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Manoranjan%20Kalia%20captured%20how%20the%20accused%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw%20lobbed%20a%20grenade%20inside%20the%20former%20minister's%20residence%20and%20the%20massive%20blast%20it%20led%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20footage%2C%20from%20around%202%20am%20today%2C%20shows%20two%20accused%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw%20driving%20by%20the%20minister's%20home.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20seen%20lobbing%20something%20over%20the%20wall.%20Another%20camera%20inside%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20home%20captures%20the%20grenade%20and%20the%20blast%20it%20causes.%20While%20no%20one%20was%20hurt%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20vehicles%20and%20windows%20of%20his%20home%20were%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20minister%20and%20former%20Punjab%20BJP%20chief%20was%20sleeping%20and%20was%20woken%20by%20a%20severe%20explosion.%20%26quot%3BThe%20grenade%20attack%20was%20so%20severe%20that%20the%20partition%20in%20the%20house%20was%20severely%20damaged.%20The%20window%20glass%20of%20the%20kitchen%20was%20damaged.%20A%20bathroom%20door%20was%20damaged%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20PTI%20report.%20Mr%20Kalia%20said%20he%20initially%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20blast%20in%20the%20electric%20transformer%20and%20later%20found%20out%20that%20it%20was%20a%20grenade%20blast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20police%20responded%20swiftly%20and%20arrested%20both%20accused%20within%2012%20hours%20of%20the%20incident.%20The%20e-rickshaw%20they%20used%20has%20also%20been%20seized.%20In%20a%20startling%20revelation%2C%20police%20found%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20masterminded%20by%20Zeeshan%20Akhtar%2C%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20and%20a%20wanted%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20NCP%20leader%20Baba%20Siddiqui%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%20Sources%20in%20the%20police%20have%20also%20said%20Pakistan's%20ISI%20has%20conspired%20to%20disrupt%20religious%20harmony%20in%20Punjab%20and%20that%20the%20attack%20against%20the%20BJP%20leader%20was%20planned%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20blasts%20in%20Punjab%20that%20has%20prompted%20Opposition%20parties%20to%20target%20the%20Bhagwant%20Singh%20Mann%20government.%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20Tarun%20Chugh%20sought%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BThe%20grenade%20attack%20on%20the%20residence%20of%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20minister%20Manoranjan%20Kalia%20is%20a%20chilling%20reminder%20of%20the%20complete%20collapse%20of%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Punjab%20under%20CM%20Bhagwant%20Mann's%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20minister%20Mohinder%20Bhagat%20earlier%20said%20people%20who%20%26quot%3Bcould%20not%20digest%20the%20all-round%20development%20of%20the%20state%26quot%3B%20were%20behind%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20blast%20at%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20home%2C%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%20terrorist%20Happy%20Passia%20has%20claimed%20responsibility.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20may%20be%20working%20with%20Khalistan%20terrorist%20outfits%20and%20the%20ISI%2C%20something%20security%20agencies%20have%20suspected%20for%20a%20while%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20year%2C%20Punjab%20has%20witnessed%20as%20many%20as%2012%20blasts%20and%20Happy%20Passia's%20name%20has%20cropped%20up%20in%20probes%20into%20the%20explosions.%20Along%20with%20him%2C%20gangster%20Jeevan%20Fauji%20is%20also%20suspected%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20attacks%2C%20many%20of%20them%20targeting%20police%20establishments%20in%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744111080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fhqqo2ltk_punjab-grenade_625x300_08_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanoranjan-kalia-caught-on-cctv-late-night-grenade-attack-at-bjp-leaders-jalandhar-home-8116413%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Footage%20from%20CCTV%20cameras%20outside%20and%20inside%20the%20Jalandhar%20home%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Manoranjan%20Kalia%20captured%20how%20the%20accused%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw%20lobbed%20a%20grenade%20inside%20the%20former%20minister's%20residence%20and%20the%20massive%20blast%20it%20led%20to.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Very%20strange'%3