%20of%20Maharashtra%20Eknath%20Shinde%20during%20a%20recent%20stand-up%20performance.%20His%20satirical%20comments%20about%20Mr%20Shinde's%20political%20choices%20sparked%20backlash%20from%20various%20groups%2C%20leading%20to%20police%20complaints%20being%20lodged%20against%20the%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%207%2C%20Kunal%20Kamra%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20post%20an%20open%20letter%20directed%20at%20BookMyShow%2C%20accusing%20the%20platform%20of%20removing%20his%20shows%20in%20response%20to%20the%20controversy.%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20he%20challenged%20the%20decision%20and%20demanded%20access%20to%20audience%20data%2C%20a%20move%20that%20sparked%20widespread%20discussions%20and%20raised%20eyebrows%20across%20digital%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20excerpt%20from%20his%20two-page%20letter%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BDear%20BookMyShow%2C%20I%20understand%20that%20you%20need%20to%20maintain%20a%20cordial%20relationship%20with%20the%20state%2C%20and%20I%20know%20that%20Mumbai%20is%20a%20major%20hub%20for%20live%20entertainment.%20Without%20the%20state's%20cooperation%2C%20iconic%20shows%20like%20Coldplay%20and%20Guns%20N'%20Roses%20wouldn't%20be%20possible...%20I%20request%20one%20of%20the%20following%3A%20Do%20not%20delist%20me%20or%20provide%20me%20with%20the%20data%20(contact%20information)%20I've%20generated%20through%20your%20platform%20from%20my%20audience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20shared%20by%20Mr%20Kamra%20on%20his%20X%20account%2C%20comes%20just%20days%20after%20Shiv%20Sena%20alleged%20that%20BookMyShow%20had%20removed%20him%20from%20both%20its%20ticket%20sales%20and%20artist%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20BookMyShow%20released%20an%20official%20statement%20to%20clarify%20the%20situation.%20Their%20statement%20mentioned%20that%20'facts%20have%20been%20misrepresented%2C'%20revealing%20their%20role%20in%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBookMyShow%20is%20a%20platform%20to%20facilitate%20the%20sale%20of%20tickets%20and%20operates%20with%20neutrality%20and%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20laws%20of%20India.%20Some%20facts%20about%20our%20role%20have%20been%20misrepresented.%20It's%20the%20organiser%20or%20the%20venue%20that%20decides%20whether%20to%20list%20or%20delist%20shows.%20We%20do%20not%20restrict%20any%20artist%20from%20selling%20their%20show%20on%20their%20website%2C%20should%20they%20choose%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20emphasised%20that%20they%20do%20not%20interfere%20with%20the%20content%20of%20performances%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20entirely%20up%20to%20the%20performers%20or%20organisers%20to%20decide%20what%20is%20presented%20on%20stage.%20%26quot%3BWe%20collaborate%20with%20different%20venues%20and%20promoters%20based%20on%20agreed%20terms.%20Artists%20are%20also%20free%20to%20sell%20tickets%20through%20their%20own%20websites%20if%20they%20choose%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20development%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20reportedly%20directed%20the%20Mumbai%20police%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20MLA%20Murji%20Patel%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Kunal%20Kamra.%20The%20comedian%20is%20challenging%20the%20FIR%20filed%20against%20him%20for%20allegedly%20making%20a%20%26quot%3Btraitor%26quot%3B%20comment%20about%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20during%20one%20of%20his%20stand-up%20comedy%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20now%20adjourned%20the%20matter%20to%20April%2016%20and%20has%20given%20the%20time%20to%20prosecution%20to%20seek%20instructions%20from%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Kamra's%20lawyer%20has%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20permit%20the%20comedian%20to%20attend%20the%20proceedings%20via%20video%20conferencing%2C%20citing%20the%20death%20threats%20he%20has%20received.%20The%20lawyer%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20client%20is%