20attack%20at%20BJP%20leader%20Manoranjan%20Kalia's%20home%20in%20Punjab's%20Jalandhar%20was%20masterminded%20by%20Zeeshan%20Akhtar%2C%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20and%20a%20wanted%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20NCP%20leader%20Baba%20Siddiqui%2C%20sources%20in%20Punjab%20police%20have%20said.%20Sources%20in%20the%20police%20have%20also%20said%20Pakistan's%20ISI%20has%20conspired%20to%20disrupt%20religious%20harmony%20in%20Punjab%20and%20that%20the%20attack%20against%20the%20BJP%20leader%20was%20planned%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20blast%20at%20the%20home%20of%20Mr%20Kalia%2C%20a%20former%20Cabinet%20minister%20and%20a%20former%20state%20BJP%20chief%2C%20early%20on%20Tuesday%20damaged%20an%20aluminum%20partition%20and%20shattered%20glass%20windows%20of%20his%20home%20and%20vehicles.%20No%20one%20was%20hurt%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20BJP%20leader%20was%20home%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20blasts%20in%20Punjab%20that%20has%20prompted%20Opposition%20parties%20to%20target%20the%20Bhagwant%20Singh%20Mann%20government.%20Punjab%20minister%20Mohinder%20Bhagat%20had%20said%20people%20who%20%26quot%3Bcould%20not%20digest%20the%20all-round%20development%20of%20the%20state%26quot%3B%20were%20behind%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20the%20main%20accused%20who%20threw%20the%20grenade%20has%20been%20taken%20into%20custody%20and%20the%20e-rickshaw%20used%20in%20the%20attack%20has%20also%20been%20seized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntererestingly%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20blast%20at%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20home%2C%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%20terrorist%20Happy%20Passia%20has%20claimed%20responsibility.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20may%20be%20working%20with%20Khalistan%20terrorist%20outfits%20and%20the%20ISI%2C%20something%20security%20agencies%20have%20suspected%20for%20a%20while%20now.%3C%2Fp%3