0was%20a%20really%20consistent%20feel%20and%20messaging%20of%20the%20type%20of%20people%20here%2C%20the%20posture%20of%20how%20they%20want%20to%20do%20business%20and%20build%20teams%20%E2%80%94%20extremely%20collaborative%20and%20collegial.%20They%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20into%20how%20they%20built%20the%20business%20to%20incentivize%20collaboration%20and%20teamwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20a%20typical%20morning%20look%20like%20inside%20the%20Lund%20household%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20home%2C%20I'm%20usually%20greeted%20by%20my%206-year-old%20daughter%20at%20about%206%3A30%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20so%20that's%20the%20perfect%20wake-up%20call.%20If%20I'm%20not%20at%20home%2C%20I'll%20still%20get%20up%20around%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20breakfast%2C%20I'm%20a%20protein%20bar%20guy%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20easy%20and%20efficient%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20have%20some%20espresso.%20If%20I%20have%20more%20time%2C%20it's%20a%20bacon%2C%20egg%2C%20sausage%20kind%20of%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20start%20my%20day%20the%20night%20before.%20I%20look%20at%20my%20calendar%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20know%20exactly%20what%20the%20day%20looks%20like%2C%20and%20what%20I%20need%20to%20prepare%20for%20%E2%80%94%20assuming%20it's%20something%20that%20I%20haven't%20already%20been%20preparing%20for%20multiple%20days%2C%20like%20a%20big%20pitch%20or%20important%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20us%20through%20an%20average%20work%20day.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20my%20mornings%20by%20triaging%20emails%20and%20reviewing%20my%20calendar.%20I%20try%20not%20to%20schedule%20any%20meetings%20before%20at%20least%209%20o'clock%2C%20preferably%2010.%20If%20I'm%20traveling%2C%20I%20try%20to%20take%20the%206%20a.m.%20flights%20so%20that%20it%20doesn't%20wreck%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wear%20multiple%20different%20hats.%20There's%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20internal%20and%20admin%20work%20that%20we%20do%2C%20including%20personnel%20factors%20that%20take%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%20We're%20meeting%20with%20the%20staffers%20to%20make%20sure%20our%20team%20is%20not%20overworked%20or%20underworked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20meetings%20throughout%20the%20day.%20I%20spend%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20my%20time%20meeting%20with%20clients%20and%20private%20equity%20sponsors.%20We%20talk%20about%20live%20deals%2C%20markets%2C%20specific%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20a%20broad%20swath%20of%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20us%20about%20the%20tech%20and%20software%20team%20at%20Houlihan.%20How%20big%20is%20it%2C%20where%20are%20people%20based%2C%20and%20how%20do%20they%20work%20together%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20is%20global%20and%20primarily%20split%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Europe.%20It%20fluctuates%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20but%20I'll%20just%20call%20it%20150%20to%20160%20people%20at%20any%20given%20time%20throughout%20the%20past%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20probably%2080%20or%2085%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20balance%20in%20Europe.%20The%20largest%20office%20in%20the%20US%20is%20New%20York%2C%20but%20we've%20got%20a%20fairly%20sizable%20office%20in%20San%20Francisco%20as%20well%20as%20some%20bankers%20like%20myself%20that%20are%20in%20neither.%20I'm%20officially%20out%20of%20our%20Miami%20office%2C%20although%20I%20tend%20to%20be%20on%20the%20road%20more%20or%20in%20Tampa%20where%20I%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEurope%20has%20the%20balance%20of%20our%20team%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20with%20a%20sizable%20presence%20in%20London%2C%20Manchester%2C%20and%20Frankfurt.%20We've%20got%20bankers%20in%20France%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20some%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20bankers%20live%20in%20geographies%20where%20there's%20a%20concentration%20of%20activity%20or%20where%20their%20focus%20is%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20selling%20an%20intangible%2C%20and%20we're%20human%20beings%20who%20communicate%20non-verbally%20in%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20ways.%20You%20can't%20replicate%20that%20through%20Zoom.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20in%20three%20dimensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWalk%20us%20through%20the%20vision%20you%20have%20for%20the%20team%20and%20its%20growth.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20could%20easily%20double%20the%20size%20of%20our%20team%20and%20commensurately%20double%20or%20more%20of%20its%20revenues.%20Call%20that%20the%20five-year%20goal.%20That's%20not%20official%2C%20but%20I%20personally%20see%20the%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20of%20that%20growth%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20from%20the%20US%20than%20Europe%2C%20just%20because%20the%20US%20is%20a%20much%20bigger%20market%20and%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20room%20to%20capture%20market%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20we%20hired%20five%20MDs%20on%20the%20technology%20team.%20We've%20not%20yet%20formalized%20our%20hiring%20plans%20for%20the%20coming%20year%2C%20but%20we%20are%20actively%20looking%20to%20hire%20additional%20senior%20folks%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20one%2C%20two%2C%20three%2C%20or%20five%20more%2C%20or%20maybe%20more%20than%20that%20TBD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhether%20in%20the%20office%20or%20working%20from%20home%2C%20how%20do%20you%20make%20the%20space%20your%20own%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20home%20office%20is%20the%20one%20that%20I%20put%20the%20most%20effort%20into.%20It's%20messier%20than%20I%20would%20like.%20I've%20got%20a%20Florida%20Gators%20helmet%20%E2%80%94%20I%20grew%20up%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20the%20Gators%2C%20and%20I'm%20excited%20because%20my%20son's%20going%20there%20%E2%80%94%20signed%20by%20Tim%20Tebow%20and%20Steve%20Spurrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20my%20oldest%20son%20both%20went%20to%20Florida%20State.%20So%20offsetting%20that%20helmet%20is%20a%20signed%20Florida%20State%20helmet%20and%20a%20ball%20from%20a%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20got%20a%20Harvard%20football%20helmet%2C%20which%20was%20from%20my%20glory%20days.%20I've%20got%20a%20bunch%20of%20my%20favorite%20deal%20trophies%20in%20the%20cabinet%2C%20which%20is%20fun%20to%20reminisce%20on%20the%20challenging%20but%20fun%20transactions.%20And%20many%20of%20those%20%E2%80%94%20I%20still%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20CEO%20or%20business%20owner%20who%20have%20become%20friends%20of%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20important%20are%20the%20pictures%20of%20my%20family%20behind%20me.%20I%20can%20always%20glance%20over%20and%20see%20my%20beautiful%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMust-have%20snack%20when%20the%20mid-afternoon%20work%20munchies%20set%20in%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20on%20the%20road%2C%20on%20average%2C%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20or%20about%20150%20nights%20a%20year.%20It's%20been%20like%20this%20for%20at%20least%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%2C%20ever%20travel%20with%20a%20backpack%20that%20doesn't%20have%20at%20least%20a%20couple%20snacks%20in%20it.%20You%20never%20know%20when%20you're%20going%20to%20miss%20a%20meal.%20Plane%20food%20is%20awful.%20I've%20got%20lots%20of%20protein%20bars%20and%20cashews%20and%20things%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20office%20snack%2C%20it%20might%20be%20popcorn.%20I'm%20definitely%20a%20fan%20of%20good%2C%20butter%20popcorn%20%E2%80%94%20not%20movie%20theater%20style%3B%20it's%20too%20salty%20%E2%80%94%20or%20it%20could%20be%20a%20KIND%20Bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20helps%20you%20manage%20stress%20and%20decompress%20after%20a%20long%20day%20or%20during%20a%20deal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20high-stress%20person.%20My%20philosophy%20in%20life%20is%20that%20every%20day%20is%20a%20privilege.%20I%20have%20strong%20faith%2C%20and%20I'm%20blessed%20to%20even%20be%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20me%2C%20when%20something's%20not%20going%20right%20in%20a%20deal%2C%20I%20can%20pretty%20easily%20reflect%20and%20be%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20this%20is%20really%20important%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20but%20this%20isn't%20actually%20what's%20most%20important%20in%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20a%20lot%20to%20rattle%20me.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20I'm%20not%20human.%20I%20get%20stressed%20during%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20moment.%20I%20like%20to%20go%20for%20long%20walks%20outside%3B%20fresh%20air%20has%20a%20way%20of%20clearing%20the%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20hobbies%3F%20Is%20there%20anything%20you%20obsess%20over%20outside%20of%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20big%20wine%20collector.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20big%20Napa%20fans%20%E2%80%94%20Napa%20is%20where%20my%20heart%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20also%20am%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Bordeaux%20and%20Burgundies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20think%20about%20which%20wines%20are%20ready%20to%20drink.%20It's%20not%20just%2C%20go%20pull%20something%20out%20and%20pop%20it.%20Sometimes%20it's%20a%2015-%20or%2020-minute%20journey%20to%20decide%20what%20to%20open%20and%20why.%20Afterwards%2C%20I%20tell%20her%20the%20story%20of%20where%20I%20got%20the%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20ask%20my%20wife%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20would%20you%20like%20to%20open%20tonight%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20she%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20pick.%26quot%3B%20Happens%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20particularly%20challenging%20deal%20you%20worked%20on%20at%20Houlihan%20or%20over%20the%20course%20of%20your%20career%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhl.com%2Fabout-us%2Ftransactions%2Fretailnext-battery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERetailNext%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20deal%20(a%20majority%20growth%20investment%20from%20Battery%20Ventures%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesswire.com%2Fnews%2Fhome%2F20250106217684%2Fen%2FRetailNext-Announces-Majority-Growth-Investment-from-Battery-Ventures%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclosed%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E)%20was%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nature%20of%20the%20company's%20VC%20shareholder%20base%20is%20what%20made%20it%20so%20complex.%20RetailNext%20had%20raised%20money%20multiple%20times%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%20%E2%80%94%20some%20very%20large%20growth%20rounds%20and%20smaller%20bridge%20rounds.%20It%20created%20what%20I%20would%20call%20a%20very%20complex%20Rubik's%20Cube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20a%20venture-funded%20business%20that%20had%20many%2C%20many%20different%20owners%20with%20different%20hold%20periods%20at%20different%20valuations%20and%20at%20various%20raises%20with%20different%20terms.%20A%20situation%20like%20that%20can%20be%20more%20challenging%20than%20if%20you%20are%20selling%20a%20business%20for%20private%20equity%20firm%20%26quot%3BA%26quot%3B%20that%20controls%2085%25%20of%20it%2C%20where%20you%20have%20one%20clear%20decision%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20year%20hasn't%20delivered%20the%20surge%20in%20M%26amp%3BA%20and%20public%20offerings%20that%20some%20were%20hoping%20for.%20What%20are%20you%20hearing%20from%20clients%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuyers%20are%20hungry%20for%20high-quality%20deals%20and%20want%20to%20put%20capital%20to%20work%2C%20primarily%20on%20the%20sponsor%20side.%20But%20we're%20seeing%20a%20meaningful%20uptick%20in%20interest%20from%20strategic%20buyers%20as%20well.%20The%20Google%2FWiz%20transaction%2C%20for%20instance%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20an%20example%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20it's%20a%20very%20high-quality%20business%2C%20sellers%20are%20moving%20more%20slowly%20to%20bring%20them%20to%20market%20because%20of%20all%20the%20uncertainty.%20Perceived%20or%20real%20%E2%80%94%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20People%20are%20being%20cautious%20and%20delaying%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20encouraging%20clients%20that%20have%20identified%20quality%20assets%20they%20like%20to%20spend%20their%20time%20wisely%20with%20doing%20the%20wo