s%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20hasn't%20chugged%20their%20little%20drink%20on%20a%20plane%20because%20there%20wasn't%20enough%20space%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20stand-alone%20cupholder%2C%20I%20could%20leisurely%20sip%20on%20my%20complimentary%20glass%20of%20white%20wine%20as%20I%20snacked%20on%20the%20peas%20and%20cracker%20snack%20and%20read%20my%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20came%20the%20dinner%20service.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20dinner%20service%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb037a69253ccddf9ad1ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20dinner%20included%20chicken%20and%20vegetables%2C%20a%20noodle%20salad%2C%20and%20cheese%20and%20crackers.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20tray%20included%20an%20entr%C3%A9e%20of%20chicken%20or%20fish%20(the%20vegetarian%20meals%20had%20already%20been%20served)%2C%20bread%2C%20a%20small%20noodle%20salad%2C%20Australian%20cheese%20and%20crackers%2C%20and%20a%20mini%20water%20bottle.%20I%20was%20surprised%20it%20came%20with%20metal%20cutlery%20rather%20than%20the%20plastic%20or%20wood%20I'm%20used%20to%20seeing%20in%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20the%20salad%2C%20which%20featured%20vermicelli%20noodles%20and%20shrimp%20cooked%20far%20more%20delicately%20than%20expected%20for%20an%20in-flight%20meal.%20The%20shrimp%20were%20plump%20and%20fresh%2C%20pairing%20well%20with%20the%20light%2C%20tangy%20dressing%20that%20covered%20each%20noodle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20for%20the%20chicken%20entr%C3%A9e%2C%20which%20was%20solid.%20The%20meat%20was%20tender%20and%20covered%20in%20sauce%2C%20while%20the%20potatoes%20were%20well-cooked%20but%20under-seasoned.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20exactly%20gourmet%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20upgrade%20from%20the%20undercooked%20pasta%20and%20rubbery%20meat%20I've%20had%20on%20many%20long-haul%20flights%20with%20US%20airlines.%20(And%20I'll%20never%20forget%20the%20tortilla%20filled%20with%20a%20cut-up%20hot%20dog.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShortly%20after%20we'd%20settled%20into%20dinner%2C%20attendants%20offered%20us%20an%20ice-cream%20sandwich%20for%20dessert.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20dessert%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb038d63d72727e198c372%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dessert%20was%20surprisingly%20delicious.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20delicious%20vanilla%20fudge%20brownie%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20the%20flight.%20It%20featured%20a%20chocolate%20crunch%20on%20the%20bottom%20that%20satisfyingly%20snapped%20with%20every%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAn%20hour%20before%20landing%2C%20we%20were%20given%20a%20hot%20snack.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb039e63d72727e198c379%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20also%20received%20a%20warm%20sandwich%20before%20landing.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20offered%20a%20choice%20between%20a%20sandwich%20with%20sweet%20potato%20and%20cheese%20or%20sweet%20chili%20chicken.%20I%20chose%20the%20latter%2C%20which%20was%20fine.%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20the%20sweet%20chili%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20nice%2C%20warm%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20had%20a%20great%20first%20experience%20on%20Singapore%20Airlines.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225374%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Singapore%20Airlines%20Airbus%