-master-recordings-to-scooter-braun-for-300-million%2Farticleshow%2F120083977.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alcatel%20to%20invest%20%2430%20mn%20to%20relaunch%20smartphone%20business%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744100762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Falcatel-to-invest-30-mn-to-relaunch-smartphone-business-in-india-125040800543_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alcatel's%20business%20is%20operated%20by%20Chinese%20firm%20TCL%20Communication%20under%20a%20trademark%20licence%20agreement%20from%20Nokia%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Falcatel-to-invest-30-mn-to-relaunch-smartphone-business-in-india-125040800543_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Suspends%20Leader%20Who%20'Purified'%20Temple%20After%20Dalit%20Congress%20MLA's%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leadership%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20suspended%20controversial%20leader%20Gyandev%20Ahuja%20from%20the%20party%20and%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%2C%20days%20after%20he%20sprinkled%20'gangajal'%20at%20a%20temple%20in%20Alwar%20to%20'purify'%20the%20premises%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Tikaram%20Jully%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20attended%20the%20temple's%20consecration%20ceremony.%3Cbr%3E%5CnDetermined%20not%20to%20let%20Gyandev%20Ahuja's%20'purification'%20stunt%20harm%20its%20prospects%20in%20eastern%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20Dalit%20voters%20play%20a%20key%20role%2C%20the%20state%20leadership%20has%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20Mr%20Ahuja.%20The%20notice%2C%20issued%20by%20BJP%20MP%20and%20senior%20Rajasthan%20leader%20Damodar%20Agarwal%2C%20has%20sought%20an%20explanation%20from%20Mr%20Ahuja%20within%20three%20days.%20The%20notice%20warns%20that%20if%20the%20former%20MLA%20does%20not%20send%20his%20response%20to%20state%20party%20chief%20Madan%20Rathore%20within%20three%20days%2C%20he%20will%20face%20disciplinary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20taking%20the%20party's%20primary%20membership%2C%20you%20took%20an%20oath%20that%20you%20will%20not%20discriminate%20based%20on%20caste%2C%20gender%20and%20religion.%20But%20you%20sprinkled%20'gangajal'%20to%20protest%20Tikaram%20Jully's%20visit.%20Your%20action%20has%20maligned%20the%20party's%20image%20and%20falls%20into%20the%20category%20of%20indiscipline%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Temple%20Visit%2C%20And%20'Purification'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20temple%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Alwar%20held%20its%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20Ramnavami%2C%20observed%20on%20Sunday.%20Among%20those%20who%20attended%20the%20event%20was%20Tika%20Ram%20Jully%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20and%20three-time%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20Alwar%20Rural.%20Earlier%2C%20Mr%20Ahuja%20then%20said%20the%20temple%20would%20become%20%26quot%3Bimpure%26quot%3B%20when%20%26quot%3Bhis%20feet%26quot%3B%20enter%20the%20temple%20and%20%26quot%3Bhis%20hands%20touch%20the%20deity%26quot%3B.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20he%20sprinkled%20'gangajal'%20to%20'purify'%20the%20temple%20and%20performed%20a%20'puja'.%20A%20video%20of%20him%20doing%20this%20went%20viral.%20When%20Congress%20leaders%20pointed%20to%20Mr%20Tully's%20Dalit%20background%20and%20said%20Mr%20Ahuja's%20actions%20reflect%20his%20casteist%20mindset%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BDalit%20supporter%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20his%20actions%20were%20against%20the%20Congress%20mindset.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20personal%20animosity%20against%20Tika%20Ram%20Jully.%20I%20also%20went%20to%20meet%20him%20on%20his%20birthday.%20But%20the%20Congress%20calls%20Ram%20Setu%20fictional%2C%20then%20why%20do%20they%20come%20to%20a%20temple%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Congress%20Reacted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jully%20said%20Mr%20Ahuja's%20remarks%20reflect%20the%20BJP's%20views%20on%20Dalits.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20an%20attack%20on%20my%20faith%20but%20a%20statement%20that%20encourages%20a%20crime%20like%20untouchability.%20Does%20BJP%20hate%20Dalits%20so%20much%20that%20they%20cannot%20see%20us%20perform%20'puja'%3F%20Do%20Gods%20only%20belong%20to%20BJP%20leaders%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20veteran%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20said%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20a%20narrow%20mindset%20is%20unacceptable%20in%20a%20civilised%20society%20in%2021st%20Century%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BDo%20Rajasthan's%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20state%20BJP%20President%20approve%20of%20such%20conduct%20by%20a%20senior%20leader%3F%20Will%20BJP%20take%20action%20against%20its%20leader%20for%20this%20despicable%20act%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20the%20BJP's%20leaders'%20actions%20insult%20the%20ideals%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20leadership%20should%20apologise%20for%20this%20shameful%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20The%20First%20Time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGyandev%20Ahuja%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Ramgarh%20MLA%20from%202013%20to%202018%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20controversies.%20He%20first%20hit%20headlines%20in%202016%20during%20the%20row%20over%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B%20slogans%20raised%20at%20JNU.%20Mr%20Ahuja%20had%20said%203%2C000%20condoms%20and%202%2C000%20liquor%20bottles%20were%20found%20on%20the%20JNU%20campus%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20defended%20the%20killing%20of%20Pehlu%20Khan%2C%20a%20dairy%20farmer%2C%20by%20cow%20vigilantes%20in%202017.%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20take%20the%20law%20into%20our%20hands.%20But%20we%20have%20no%20regret%20over%20his%20death%20because%20those%20who%20are%20cow-smugglers%20are%20cow-killers%2C%20sinners%20like%20them%20have%20met%20this%20fate%20earlier%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahuja%20had%20said.%20He%20had%20also%20said%20that%20anyone%20smuggling%20cows%20should%20be%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744100760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ff989gpao_gyandev-ahuja_625x300_08_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyandev-ahuja-bjp-suspends-leader-who-purified-temple-after-dalit-congress-mlas-visit-8115109%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20leadership%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20suspended%20controversial%20leader%20Gyandev%20Ahuja%20from%20the%20party%20and%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%2C%20after%20he%20sprinkled%20'gangajal'%20at%20a%20temple%20to%20'purify'%20the%20premises%20after%20Congress'%20leader%20Tikaram%20Jully%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20visited%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyandev-ahuja-bjp-suspends-leader-who-purified-temple-after-dalit-congress-mlas-visit-8115109%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Motors%20global%20wholesales%20decline%203%25%20to%20366%2C177%20units%20in%20Q4%20FY25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744100424000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-motors-global-wholesales-decline-3-to-366-177-units-in-q4-fy25-125040800557_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Global%20wholesales%20of%20Tata%20Motors%20passenger%20vehicles%2C%20including%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20in%20Q4%20FY25%20were%20at%20146%2C999%20units%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-motors-global-wholesales-decline-3-to-366-177-units-in-q4-fy25-125040800557_1.html%22%2C%22