F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECan%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%20be%20another%20turning%20point%20in%20Indian%20history%2C%20just%20as%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20episode%20proved%20to%20be%20in%20the%201980s%3F%20Following%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20ruling%20in%20favour%20of%20Shah%20Bano%2C%20which%20mandated%20that%20she%20be%20granted%20maintenance%20by%20her%20husband%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20civil%20law%20of%20the%20country%2C%20many%20Muslims%20viewed%20the%20judgment%20as%20an%20intrusion%20into%20their%20religious%20and%20personal%20affairs.%20The%20decision%20sparked%20widespread%20anger%20within%20the%20community%2C%20leading%20to%20large-scale%20protests%20on%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20journalist%20Neerja%20Chowdhury%2C%20in%20her%20book%20%3Cem%3EHow%20Prime%20Ministers%20Decide%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%20protested%20on%20the%20streets%20in%20their%20lakhs%2C%20holding%20demonstrations%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Patna%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Hyderabad%20and%20other%20cities.%20This%20also%20exerted%20its%20own%20pressure%20on%20the%20AIMPLB%20%5BAll%20India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%5D.%E2%80%9D%20She%20further%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9CThese%20protests%20in%201985%20were%20the%20first%20real%20signs%20of%20large-scale%20assertiveness%20by%20Muslims%20after%20independence.%20There%20had%20been%20demonstrations%20by%20the%20community%20earlier%2C%20of%20course...%20But%20there%20had%20never%20been%20anything%20to%20compare%20with%20the%20outrage%20that%20erupted%20after%20the%20judgment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20a%20different%20country.%20Muslim%20leaders%20employed%20hyperbole%20and%20delivered%20provocative%20speeches%20that%20unsettled%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20of%20the%20era.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20serving%20as%20prime%20minister%20with%20an%20unprecedented%20mandate%2C%20was%20advised%20to%20course-correct%20to%20avoid%20losing%20Muslim%20support.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20Congress%20made%20a%20decision%20that%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20history.%20The%20Rajiv%20government%20introduced%20a%20bill%20in%20Parliament%2C%20which%2C%20given%20the%20party's%20historic%20mandate%2C%20was%20easily%20passed%20to%20restore%20the%20earlier%20position%20regarding%20Islamic%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Shah%20Bano%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Shah%20Bano%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ftksqcj4g_shah-bano-rajiv-gandhi_625x300_08_April_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government's%20decision%20in%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20case%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20history%20and%20gave%20the%20RSS%20a%20long-awaited%20opportunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20move%20created%20another%20issue.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20was%20relatively%20weak%2C%20but%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20through%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%2C%20was%20working%20to%20make%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20a%20significant%20issue.%20The%20Shah%20Bano%20case%20gave%20the%20RSS%20a%20long-awaited%20opportunity%2C%20presenting%20a%20compelling%20argument%20for%20their%20campaign%20against%20what%20they%20perceived%20as%20appeasement%20politics.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20campaign%20began%20gaining%20traction.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20Rajiv's%20cousin%20and%20influential%20leader%2C%20Arun%20Nehru%2C%20advised%20him%20to%20placate%20Hindus%20to%20avoid%20losing%20their%20support.%20Chowdhury%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Rajiv%20persisted%20in%20placating%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20Nehru%20warned%2C%20it%20could%20cost%20him%20his%20%E2%80%98support%20base%20among%20Hindus'%20which%20%E2%80%98was%20becoming%20shaky'.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ENehru's%20Three%20Suggestions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20return%20to%20power%2C%20you%20will%20need%20to%20do%20three%20things%3A%20build%20a%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20enact%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20and%20abrogate%20Article%20370%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20This%20was%20Nehru's%20advice%20to%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20Chowdhury's%20book.%20Ultimately%2C%20Gandhi%20succumbed%20to%20the%20pressure%2C%20and%20on%20February%201%2C%201986%2C%20the%20locks%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20were%20opened.%20The%20book%20also%20suggests%20that%20then-RSS%20leader%20Bhaurao%20Devras%20had%20given%20Gandhi%20a%20similar%20advice.%20Chowdhury%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Janmabhoomi%20ka%20tala%20kholo%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20Bhaurao%20had%20sent%20Rajiv%20word%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHinduon%20ke%20neta%20Bano%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(open%20the%20locks%20and%20become%20a%20leader%20of%20Hindus).%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20should%20have%20refrained%20from%20both%20actions%20-%20from%20interfering%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20on%20Shah%20Bano%2C%20as%20well%20as%20from%20allowing%20the%20temple%20locks%20to%20be%20opened.%20He%20should%20have%20let%20history%20take%20its%20own%20course.%20In%20the%201989%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20lost%20power%20and%20VP%20Singh%20became%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20with%20Arun%20Nehru%20part%20of%20his%20cabinet.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20never%20secured%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20Parliament.%20These%20events%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20does%20not%20imply%20that%20history%20will%20necessarily%20follow%20the%20same%20trajectory%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EParallels%20Today%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20recounting%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20case%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20recognise%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20moment.%20History%20has%20its%20own%20way%20of%20unfolding.%20Two%20distinct%20parallels%20can%20be%20drawn%20from%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20episode%3A%20first%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20then%2C%20Muslims%20today%20feel%20that%20the%20state%20is%20interfering%20in%20their%20religious%20and%20personal%20matters.%20Second%2C%20just%20as%20then%2C%20there%20is%20visible%20anger%20within%20the%20community%20today%2C%20evidenced%20by%20the%20public%20protests%20against%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Supporters%20attend%20the%20All%20India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20(AIMPLB)%20protest%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20March.%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Supporters%20attend%20the%20All%20India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20(AIMPLB)%20protest%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20March.%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fcif86h6g_waqf_625x300_08_April_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20attend%20the%20All%20India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20(AIMPLB)%20protest%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20March.%20%3Cem%3E(%3Cspan%3EANI)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20pre-Ram%20Mandir-movement%20era%2C%20the%20Muslim%20leadership%20in%20India%20was%20undoubtedly%20influential%2C%20and%20their%20voices%20were%20heard.%20They%20were%20assertive%2C%20and%20the%20political%20system%2C%20dominated%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20was%20receptive%20to%20their%20concerns.%20However%2C%20this%20did%20not%20necessarily%20translate%20into%20better%20economic%20conditions%20for%20the%20community.%20While%20they%20had%20greater%20political%20influence%2C%20this%20did%20not%20equate%20to%20economic%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrewing%20Discontent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20their%20bargaining%20power%20has%20diminished%20a%20great%20deal.%20The%20ruling%20BJP%20appears%20indifferent%20to%20their%20concerns%2C%20despite%20rhetoric%20like%20'%3Cem%3ESabka%20Sath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas%3C%2Fem%3E'%20or%20gestures%20such%20as%20'%3Cem%3EModi%20ki%20Saugat%3C%2Fem%3E'%20on%20Eid.%20The%20BJP%20openly%20engages%20in%20Hindutva%20politics%20and%20does%20not%20have%20a%20Muslim%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20same%20holds%20true%20in%20states%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20either%20in%20power%20or%20opposition.%20It%20is%20ironic%20that%20the%20party%20that%20introduced%20the%20Waqf%20bill%20in%20Parliament%20had%20no%20Muslim%20MP%20to%20speak%20on%20an%20issue%20directly%20affecting%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20has%20shown%20remarkable%20patience%20so%20far%2C%20with%20reactions%20becoming%20increasingly%20rare.%20Silence%20has%20been%20their%20armour.%20Apart%20from%20the%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20movement%2C%20the%20community%20has%20largely%20refrained%20from%20taking%20to%20the%20streets.%20They%20have%20even%20stopped%20responding%20to%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20aggressive%20posturing%20and%20have%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20influence%20of%20Muslim%20clerics.%20A%20new%20urban%2C%20literate%2C%20middle-class%20leadership%20is%20emerging%2C%20prioritising%20education%20and%20self-improvement.%20There%20is%20a%20growing%20consensus%20within%20the%20community%20that%20this%20storm%2C%20too%2C%20shall%20pass.%20Until%20then%2C%20they%20believe%20it%20is%20best%20to%20lie%20low%2C%20avoid%20provocation%2C%20steer%20clear%20of%20politics%2C%20and%20focus%20their%20energies%20on%20economic%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20now%2C%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%20episode%20threatens%20to%20disrupt%20this%20fragile%20understanding.%20If%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20could%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20co-founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satyahindi.com%2F%5C%22%3ESatyaHindi%3C%2Fa%3E%20a