%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaran-oberoi-rape-case-mumbai-court-upholds-legal-proceedings-against-pooja-bedi-and-other-celebrities%2Farticleshow%2F120088470.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Some%20Cats%20Trigger%20Allergies%20More%20Than%20Others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAllergies%20can%20be%20debilitating%20for%20those%20who%20have%20them%20-%20even%20more%20so%20when%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20allergic%20reaction%20is%20a%20beloved%20pet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faacijournal.biomedcentral.com%2Farticles%2F10.1186%2Fs13223-018-0239-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecond%20only%20to%20dust%20mites%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20humble%20domestic%20house%20cat%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8127422%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20major%20causes%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20indoor%20allergens%20for%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20the%20actual%20source%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwhat-are-allergies-and-why-are-we-getting-more-of-them-40318%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20allergic%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20And%20are%20certain%20breeds%20less%20allergenic%20than%20others%3F%20There%20are%20many%20myths%20and%20misconceptions%20related%20to%20cat%20allergens%2C%20so%20let's%20debunk%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20the%20hair!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20common%20misconception%2C%20cat%20hair%20is%20not%20the%20cause%20of%20allergies%20in%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20the%20breed%2C%20either%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20research%20has%20shown%20that%20neither%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31135257%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20length%20of%20the%20cat's%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20nor%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0091674901700504%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20colour%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20coat%2C%20appear%20to%20have%20any%20significant%20bearing%20on%20how%20much%20allergen%20the%20cat%20produces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20a%20cat's%20breed%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F8765830%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esex%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC6764004%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindividual%20variation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20production%20of%20Fel%20d%201%20are%20the%20main%20reason%20why%20some%20cats%20seem%20to%20cause%20a%20greater%20allergic%20response%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20long%20been%20known%20that%20on%20average%2C%20unneutered%20male%20cats%20produce%20more%20Fel%20d%201%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F8765830%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethan%20females%20or%20neutered%20males%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31135257%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESome%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20found%20that%20older%20cats%20tend%20to%20produce%20lower%20levels%20of%20Fel%20d%201%20than%20younger%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20breeds%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.petmd.com%2Fcat%2Fgeneral-health%2Fhypoallergenic-cat-breeds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehypoallergenic%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20%26quot%3Ballergen-free%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20a%20review%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10975736%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20date%2C%20there%20is%20no%20scientific%20evidence%20for%20a%20hypoallergenic%20cat%20breed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20putting%20our%20strict%20hypoallergenic%20definition%20aside%2C%20a%20few%20small%20studies%20have%20reported%20reduced%20levels%20of%20Fel%20d%201%20production%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1186%2F2045-7022-4-S2-P11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20of%20these%20breeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20though%20that%20even%20in%20individual%20cats%2C%20production%20of%20Fel%20d%201%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31135257%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evary%20widely%20throughout%20the%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20studies%20in%20these%20breeds%2C%20using%20larger%20sample%20sizes%2C%20is%20needed%20to%20confirm%20these%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20sensitive%20people%20report%20an%20increased%20allergic%20response%20to%20some%20cats%20rather%20than%20others%20is%20likely%20due%20to%20variation%20in%20how%20much%20Fel%20d%201%20the%20individual%20cat%20produces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20several%20studies%20have%20investigated%20the%20possibility%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1038%2Fd41586-020-02779-3%5C%22%3Evaccinating%20cats%20against%20the%20Fel%20d%201%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20would%20be%20great%20news%20for%20allergy%20sufferers%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20researchers%20are%20currently%20unsure%20what%20role%20the%20protein%20plays%20in%20cats.%20Current%20evidence%20suggests%20it%20may%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20dispersal%20of%20pheromones%2C%20and%20potentially%20in%20protecting%20the%20cat's%20skin%3B%20further%20research%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31310154%2F%5C%22%3Esome%20initial%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20suggest%20that%20therapeutic%20diets%20in%20which%20an%20antibody%20is%20added%20from%20chicken%20eggs%20(IgY%20antibodies)%20can%20reduce%20the%20production%20of%20Fel%20d%201%20that%20a%20cat%20produces.%20However%2C%20larger%20studies%20are%20needed%20before%20we%20might%20start%20seeing%20%26quot%3Banti-allergy%26quot%3B%20cat%20food%20on%20the%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20some%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20exposure%20to%20cats%20at%20a%20young%20age%20may%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20person%20developing%20an%20allergy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20an%20adult%20allergic%20to%20cats%20but%20still%20would%20like%20to%20have%20one%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fall.14013%5C%22%3Ethere%20is%20good%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20suggest%20regular%20cleaning%20can%20substantially%20decrease%20the%20amount%20of%20cat%20allergens%20in%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20jury%20is%20out%20on%20the%20scientific%20evidence%20for%20%26quot%3Bhypoallergenic%26quot%3B%20cat%20breeds%2C%20some%20cats%20really%20are%20less%20allergenic%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20for%20those%20that%20are%20allergic%2C%20you%20are%20not%20doomed%20to%20have%20to%20avoid%20cats%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life.%20With%20the%20right%20management%20and%20care%2C%20cat%20ownership%20is%20entirely%20possible%20-%20and%20absolutely%20worth%20it.%3Cim