Fpriyanka-chopras-mother-madhu-chopra-and-brother-siddharth-rent-out-pune-property-for-rs-2-25-lakh-per-month-to-earn-rs-1-5-crore-in-five-years%2Farticleshow%2F120088464.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Byju%20Raveendran%20files%20FIR%2C%20says%20%E2%80%98I%20am%20not%20a%20flower%2C%20I%20am%20the%20fire%20that%20will%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744097726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120088415%2Cimgsize-27692.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fbyju-raveendran-files-fir-against-resolution-professional-ey-partners-says-i-am-not-a-flower-i-am-the-fire-that-will%2Farticleshow%2F120088309.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Byju%20Raveendran%20has%20filed%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20against%20Pankaj%20Srivastava%2C%20the%20former%20resolution%20professional%2C%20Glas%20Trust%2C%20and%20EY%20employees%2C%20alleging%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20BYJU'S.%20This%20action%20follows%20claims%20of%20EY's%20collaboration%20with%20Glas%20Trust%20during%20insolvency%20proceedings.%20Raveendran%20accuses%20them%20of%20prioritizing%20lenders'%20interests%20and%20concealing%20evidence%20of%20misconduct%2C%20escalating%20the%20ongoing%20financial%20dispute.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fbyju-raveendran-files-fir-against-resolution-professional-ey-partners-says-i-am-not-a-flower-i-am-the-fire-that-will%2Farticleshow%2F120088309.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Is%20Quietly%20Revoking%20Student%20Visas%20From%20Harvard%20To%20Stanford%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20immigration%20authorities%20have%20revoked%20a%20spate%20of%20student%20visas%20for%20foreign%20nationals%20at%20major%20colleges%20including%20Harvard%