campuses%2C%20including%20UCLA%2C%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20UC%20Davis%2C%20UC%20San%20Diego%2C%20UC%20Santa%20Cruz%20as%20well%20as%20Stanford%2C%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20reported%20on%20Monday.%20Two%20unidentified%20students%20have%20filed%20lawsuits%20in%20federal%20court%20alleging%20their%20visas%20were%20canceled%20without%20due%20process%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20over%20minor%20legal%20infractions%20such%20as%20driving%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20university%20learned%20of%20six%20students%20who%20had%20their%20student%20visas%20revoked%2C%26quot%3B%20Stanford%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday.%20A%20university%20working%20group%20on%20immigration%20continues%20to%20meet%2C%20and%20the%20school%20said%20it%20does%20not%20share%20student%20or%20personnel%20records%20with%20immigration%20authorities%20unless%20legally%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarvard%20reported%20on%20Sunday%20that%20three%20current%20Harvard%20students%20and%20two%20recent%20graduates%20had%20their%20student%20visas%20terminated.%20Additional%20cancellations%20have%20been%20reported%20at%20Dartmouth%20College%2C%20Minnesota%20State%20University%2C%20Arizona%20State%20University%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Oregon%2C%20among%20other%20schools%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20the%20State%20Department%20and%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20has%20long%20had%20the%20authority%20to%20revoke%20visas%2C%20but%20Dalal-Dheini%20said%20the%20current%20wave%20appears%20to%20be%20broader%20and%20more%20coordinated%20than%20past%20enforcement%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisa%20cancellations%20were%20among%20the%20many%20issues%20spotlighted%20April%205%20by%20anti-Trump%20protesters%20at%20rallies%20in%20dozens%20of%20US%20cities.%20Some%20organizers%20pointed%20to%20the%20cases%20of%20Oztur