l%20opportunity%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20rising%20electricity%20bills%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20upcoming%20peak%20summer%20months.%20By%20installing%20rooftop%20solar%20panels%2C%20homeowners%20can%20generate%20their%20own%20electricity%20and%20reduce%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F403520%2Fsnl-energy-solutions-provide-solar-power-to-impoverished-homes-in-rural-manipur-empower-women-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20power%20grid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20government%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Suryodaya%20Yojana%2C%20the%20shift%20to%20solar%20power%20has%20become%20more%20accessible.%20The%20scheme%20offers%20subsidies%20covering%20up%20to%2060%25%20of%20installation%20costs%20and%20provides%20loan%20support%20for%20the%20remaining%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstalling%20solar%20power%20is%20surprisingly%20simple.%20Modern%20photovoltaic%20(PV)%20panels%20can%20be%20fitted%20on%20rooftops%20that%20receive%20adequate%20sunlight%20and%20require%20minimal%20maintenance.%20A%20typical%20solar%20panel%20has%20a%20lifespan%20of%2025%20to%2030%20years%2C%20making%20it%20a%20long-term%20investment.%20Additionally%2C%20net%20metering%20policies%20let%20you%20sell%20excess%20electricity%20back%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20earning%20credits%20on%20your%20power%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20cost%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20talk%20numbers.%20The%20cost%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstalling%20a%20solar%20panel%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20ranges%20from%20Rs%2045%2C000%20to%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20kilowatt%20(kW)%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20quality%2C%C2%A0%20location%2C%20and%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20small%20household%20using%20around%20200%20to%20300%20units%20of%20electricity%20per%20month%20may%20require%20a%202%20kW%20system%2C%20costing%20around%20Rs%201.5%20to%202%20lakh%20upfront.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELarger%20homes%20consuming%20400%20to%20600%20units%20per%20month%20might%20need%20a%205%20kW%20system%2C%20costing%20Rs%203.5%20to%20Rs%204.5%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20investment%20typically%20pays%20for%20itself%20in%20four%20to%20six%20years%20through%20monthly%20savings%20on%20electricity%20bills.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%205%20kW%20system%20can%20generate%20around%20400%20to%20600%20units%20per%20month.%20If%20your%20average%20bill%20is%20around%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20switching%20to%20solar%20could%20cut%20it%20down%20to%20Rs%201%2C500%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20eliminate%20it%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20leading%20to%20annual%20savings%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20get%20started%20with%20rooftop%20solar%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20made%20the%20process%20simple%20through%20the%20official%20portal%20for%20the%20PM%20Surya%20Ghar%3A%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana.%20