p%E2%80%99s%20tariff%20announcements.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc70ze6reykno%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Germany%20May%20Be%20The%20Next%20Big%20Thing%20For%20Young%20Indians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20German%20parliament%20gave%20the%20green%20light%20to%20a%20record-breaking%20financial%20push%20-%20massive%20loans%20designed%20to%20supercharge%20its%20military%2C%20modernise%20its%20creaking%20infrastructure%20and%20fast-track%20climate%20protection.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20boldest%20moves%20in%20post-war%20German%20history.%20But%20big%20ambitions%20and%20deep%20pockets%20alone%20cannot%20guarantee%20success.%20For%20Germany's%20transformation%20to%20truly%20take%20off%2C%20it%20needs%20speed%20and%20a%20huge%20pool%20of%20talented%20workforce.%20The%20%E2%82%AC500%20billion%20stimulus%20needs%20a%20serious%20influx%20of%20skilled%20professionals%20to%20get%20things%20moving%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20India's%20incredible%20talent%20pool%20could%20come%20into%20play.%20For%20young%20Indians%20exploring%20opportunities%20abroad%20-%20whether%20it's%20for%20study%20or%20work%20-%20Germany's%20ambitious%20reinvention%20might%20just%20be%20the%20most%20exciting%2C%20under-the-radar%20opportunity%20for%20some%20years.%20With%20the%20right%20focus%20and%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20mindset%20shift%2C%20this%20moment%20could%20offer%20more%20than%20just%20jobs%20-%20it%20could%20be%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20part%20of%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20Europe's%20largest%20economy.%20Read%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Meeting%20In%202013%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202013%2C%20I%20struck%20up%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20German%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20in%20Hannover%2C%20a%20city%20best%20known%20for%20its%20ties%20to%20Volkswagen%20and%20the%20global%20automobile%20industry.%20He%20spoke%20passionately%20about%20India.%20Not%20only%20had%20he%20visited%20every%20Indian%20state%2C%20but%20he%20was%20in%20fact%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20persuade%20young%20Indians%20to%20look%20beyond%20the%20traditional%20English-speaking%20destinations%20-%20UK%2C%20US%2C%20Canada%20-%20and%20consider%20Germany%20for%20higher%20education%20and%20meaningful%20careers.%20His%20vision%20was%20bold%3A%20an%20India-Germany%20tech%20partnership%20that%20could%20rival%20the%20magic%20of%20Silicon%20Valley.%20He%20kept%20urging%20Indian%20youth%20to%20invest%20their%20time%20in%20learning%20German%20instead%20of%20or%20besides%20English.%20In%20his%20eyes%2C%20German%20was%20more%20than%20just%20a%20language%20-%20it%20was%20the%20gateway%20to%20real%2C%20long-term%20opportunity%20in%20Europe's%20economic%20powerhouse.%20And%20he%20wasn't%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20later%2C%20I%20had%20a%20conversation%20that%20brought%20his%20words%20back%20to%20life.%20A%20driver%20at%20a%20Delhi-based%20media%20company%20approached%20me%20for%20advice%20about%20his%20son's%20future.%20The%20boy%20was%20an%20average%20student%20and%20unsure%20of%20his%20path.%20I%20suggested%20he%20learn%20German%20and%20apply%20to%20one%20of%20Germany's%20many%20tuition-free%20universities.%20The%20same%20young%20man%20is%20now%20a%20sought-after%20professional%20in%20Germany's%20tech%20sector.%20It's%20one%20story%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20I%20have%20seen%20similar%20journeys%20unfold%2C%20even%20within%20my%20own%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20Connect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20from%20the%20German%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20jokingly%20but%20tellingly%20even%20brought%20up%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20as%20an%20example%2C%20a%20name%20that%20was%20beginning%20to%20resonate%20in%20Germany%20around%202010%20onwards%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20string%20of%20Bollywood%20hits%20shown%20on%20a%20German%20TV%20channel.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20Khan%20effected%20a%20subtle%20but%20smart%20shift%20in%20mindset%3A%20instead%20of%20focusing%20solely%20on%20the%20English-speaking%20world%2C%20he%20leaned%20into%20Europe%2C%20and%20it%20paid%20off.%20By%20accepting%20an%20invitation%20to%20the%20Berlin%20Film%20Festival%2C%20he%20opened%20the%20door%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20audience.%20That%20appearance%20sparked%20real%20interest%2C%20earned%20him%20recognition%2C%20and%20helped%20him%20carve%20out%20a%20space%20for%20Indian%20cinema%20in%20the%20European%20imagination.%20It%20was%20proof%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20even%20a%20small%20pivot%20towards%20Germany%20could%20open%20big%20doors.%20%E2%80%98SRK'%20did%20not%20need%20to%20learn%20German%20to%20become%20famous%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Germany%20Is%20Struggling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20colonial%20legacy%20still%20tugs%20at%20us.%20English%20is%20the%20default%20dream.%20We%20naturally%20gravitate%20towards%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Canada%2C%20especially%20since%2C%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20has%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20shaping%20Silicon%20Valley's%20digital%20and%20AI%20revolutions.%20But%20while%20that%20India-US%20partnership%20changed%20the%20world%2C%20Germany%2C%20despite%20its%20might%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20largely%20missed%20the%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20the%20consequences%20are%20showing.%20Once%20known%20as%20an%20industrial%20powerhouse%2C%20today's%20Germany%20is%20struggling%20with%20outdated%20infrastructure%20and%20sluggish%20innovation.%20Here's%20an%20unbelievable%20statistic%3A%20in%202023%2C%20a%20staggering%2082%25%20of%20German%20businesses%20were%20still%20using%20fax%20machines.%20And%20its%20fibre%20broadband%20rollout%20is%20among%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20OECD%20(mostly%20made%20up%20of%20big-%20and%20medium-sized%20economies).%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20this%20digital%20lag%20is%20hurting%20its%20global%20competitiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGermany%20was%20trundling%20along%2C%20despite%20the%20obvious%20problems%20with%20its%20economy.%20Then%20came%20the%20geopolitical%20wake-up%20call%2C%20when%20the%20Trump%20administration%20excluded%20Germany%20-%20and%20the%20broader%20EU%20-%20from%20talks%20on%20a%20future%20Ukraine-Russia%20peace%20settlement.%20The%20Germans%2C%20betrayed%20and%20bewildered%2C%20got%20the%20message%20loud%20and%20clear%3A%20the%20era%20of%20relying%20on%20American%20protectionism%20was%20over.%20Feeling%20blindsided%2C%20Germany%20realised%20it%20had%20to%20stand%20on%20its%20own%20feet%2C%20militarily%2C%20economically%20and%20digitally.%20Some%20of%20the%20German%20journalists%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20stance%20was%20a%20watershed%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoment%20Of%20Reckoning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Germany%20unveiled%20a%20jaw-dropping%20%E2%82%AC500%20billion%20stimulus%20package%20to%20rebuild%20its%20economy%20and%20reboot%20its%20military.%20Ambitious%2C%20no%20doubt.%20But%20this%20was%20not%20a%20partisan%20push%3B%20it%20had%20cross-party%20backing%20and%20sailed%20through%20parliament.%20The%20reforms%20aim%20to%20reverse%20years%20of%20underinvestment%20and%20recession%2C%20while%20ushering%20in%20a%20new%20age%20of%20European%20collective%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20agree%20that%20these%20moves%20were%20long%20overdue.%20And%20if%20executed%20well%2C%20they%20could%20not%20only%20reinforce%20Germany's%20leadership%20in%20Europe%20but%20also%20unlock%20serious%20opportunities%20in%20sectors%20like%20energy%2C%20transport%2C%20construction%20and%20digital%20infrastructure.%20There's%20a%20growing%20belief%20that%20this%20bold%20stimulus%20could%20spark%20a%20new%20cycle%20of%20economic%20growth%2C%20not%20just%20for%20Germany%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there's%20one%20make-or-break%20factor%3A%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20just%20a%20financial%20project%2C%20but%20a%20once-in-a-generation%20opportunity%2C%20as%20a%20German%20friend%20put%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20Germany%20needs%20engineers%2C%20builders%2C%20tech%20experts%2C%20urban%20planners%2C%20innovators%20and%20creators.%20Without%20the%20right%20hands%20and%20minds%2C%20even%20the%20most%20visionary%20plans%20will%20remain%20stuck%20on%20paper.%20The%20stakes%20are%20high%2C%20but%20so%20is%20the%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan's%20success%20will%20depend%20on%20people%2C%20not%20just%20policy.%20Skilled%20professionals%2C%20such%20as%20engineers%2C%20tech%20experts%2C%20builders%20and%20innovators%2C%20will%20be%20the%20real%20drivers%20of%20this%20progress.%20Without%20them%2C%20even%20the%20boldest%20infrastructure%20and%20green%20energy%20projects%20could%20stall%20before%20they%20take%20off.%20That's%20why%20finding%20and%20developing%20the%20right%20talent%20isn't%20just%20important%2C%20it%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Can%20Fill%20A%20Gap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20right%20now%2C%20Germany%20is%20facing%20acute%20talent%20shortages%2C%20which%20have%20been%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20its%20population%20is%20ageing.%20It%20needs%20young%20people%20who%20can%20transform%20its%20ageing%20economy.%20It%20is%20looking%20for%20its%20Silicon%20Valley%20moment.%20For%20young%20professionals%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20India%2C%20this%20is%20a%20golden%20window.%20Whether%20you%20are%20coding%20software%2C%20designing%20bridges%2C%20working%20on%20AI%2C%20or%20studying%20climate%20science%2C%20your%20skills%20are%20in%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20massive%20stimulus%20plan%20was%20approved%2C%20Germany's%20workforce%20shortages%20had%20crossed%205%20lakh.%20Organisations%20like%20the%20Association%20of%20German%20Engineers%20are%20already%20raising%20red%20flags%20about%20the%20talent%20shortage.%20According%20to%20the%20German%20media%2C%20experts%20estimate%20that%20to%20implement%20the%20massive%20plan%2C%20Germany%20will%20likely%20need%20a%20significant%20influx%20of%20both%20skilled%20labour%20and%20general%20workers%2C%20particularly%20in%20sectors%20like%20renewable%20energy%20and%20digitalisation%2C%20potentially%20requiring%20over%202.8%20lakh%20foreign%20workers%20annually%20until%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20under%20the%20India-Germany%20Migration%20and%20Mobility%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(MMPA)%2C%20which%20came%20into%20force%20on%20March%207%2C%202023%2C%20Germany%20has%20committed%20to%20increasing%20the%20annual%20visas%20for%20skilled%20Indian%20workers%20from%2020%2C000%20to%2090%2C000.%20This%20increase%20in%20visa%20allocations%20for%20Indian%20professionals%20is%20a%20strategic%20move%20to%20help%20mitigate%20Germany's%20skilled%20labour%20shortages.%20But%20with%20the%20latest%20whopping%20stimulus%2C%20this%20number%20is%20likely%20to%20increase%20by%20leaps%20and%20bounds%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20As%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20there%20is%20one%20key%20that%20will%20unlock%20the%20door%20to%20all%20these%20opportunities%20in%20Germany%3A%20the%20German%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744095360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fq7gosolo_gggggg_625x300_25_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-germany-may-be-the-