22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268152%2Fmaharashtra-village-manyachiwadi-solar-gram-electricity-sustainable-women-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Manyachiwadi%20village%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadvocates%20for%20a%20similar%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20set%20a%20precedent%20becoming%20the%20first%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20be%20100%20percent%20electrified%20by%20solar.%20Almost%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20when%20conventional%20energy%20was%20reigning%20the%20scene%2C%20Manyachiwadi%20subverted%20the%20trend%20by%20transitioning%20to%20solar.%20They%20started%20small.%20The%20women%20of%20the%20village%20began%20pooling%20in%20Rs%20100%20every%20month%20until%20the%20sum%20was%20enough%20to%20install%20solar%20systems%20in%20their%20homes.%20Today%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20a%20rupee%20for%20electricity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20world%20beyond%20the%20panels%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooftop%20solar%20and%20microgrids%20are%20fantastic.%20But%2C%20while%20advocating%20for%20these%2C%20entrepreneurs%20see%20potential%20in%20solar%20devices%20such%20as%20solar%20dryers%2C%20biogas%20grids%20and%20water%20pumps.%20These%20are%20a%20great%20way%20to%20ease%20villages%20into%20the%20world%20of%20renewable%20energy.%20And%20once%20they%20see%20how%20lucrative%20solar%20is%2C%20it%20might%20convince%20them%20to%20invest%20in%20panels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatika%20Patil%20from%20Dahanu%2C%20Maharashtra%20is%20one%20example.%20She%20belongs%20to%20a%20family%20that%20has%20been%20cultivating%20chickoo%20for%20around%2050%20years.%20But%20the%20harvest%20would%20spoil%20when%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20as%20many%20buyers.%20After%20her%20retirement%20in%202015%2C%20Latika%20took%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20the%20processing%20of%20fruits.%20At%20first%2C%20she%20resorted%20to%20sun-drying%20them%20but%20soon%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20%3Ca%20