3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20becoming%20increasingly%20common%20to%20hear%20of%20someone%20in%20their%2030s%20or%20early%2040s%20who%20had%20a%20heart%20scare%20%E2%80%94%20often%20out%20of%20the%20blue%20and%20with%20no%20obvious%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20India%2C%20doctors%20are%20reporting%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20heart%20attacks%20among%20young%20adults%2C%20challenging%20long-held%20beliefs%20that%20heart%20disease%20is%20a%20concern%20only%20for%20older%20people.%20As%20lifestyles%20evolve%20and%20risk%20factors%20shift%2C%20this%20growing%20trend%20is%20prompting%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20hidden%20impact%20of%20modern%20living%20on%20cardiovascular%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20from%20hospitals%20across%20India%2C%20between%202020%20and%202023%2C%2050%25%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-heart-attacks-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20attack%20patients%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20below%20the%20age%20of%2040.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhakar%20Rao%20M%2C%20Consultant%20Cardiologist%20at%20Manipal%20Hospital%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20confirms%20this%20worrying%20pattern.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20heart%20attacks%20were%20traditionally%20seen%20in%20people%20beyond%2050%20or%2060.%20But%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20it%20become%20very%20common%20among%20young%20adults%2C%20particularly%20those%20under%2045.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20are%20young%20people%20at%20risk%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20causes%20of%20heart%20disease%20are%20multifactorial%20%E2%80%94%20with%20genetic%20predisposition%2C%20lifestyle%20choices%2C%20and%20environmental%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20all%20playing%20a%20role.%20While%20some%20risk%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20family%20history%2C%20are%20unavoidable%2C%20many%20others%20can%20be%20managed%20or%20prevented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20most%20significant%20contributors%20is%20smoking%2C%20including%20both%20active%20and%20passive%20smoking.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20think%20that%20only%20active%20smoking%20was%20harmful%2C%20but%20even%20passive%20smoking%20is%20a%20serious%20risk%20factor%20for%20heart%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20person%20holding%20a%20cigarette%20in%20hand%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418279%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESmoking%2C%20both%20active%20and%20passive%2C%20increases%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20cardiac%20disease%20at%20scale.%20Image%20credits%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fmrbo2ykgx5lt%2F22341%2F5535f080e1a7bb67f5fbb382d2295c7c%2Fcigarette-lung-bowel-inflammation.jpg%3F%26w%3D912%26fm%3Dwebp%26q%3D80%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrontiers.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmoking%20causes%20vasoconstriction%2C%20which%20means%20the%20blood%20vessels%20become%20narrow%20and%20tight.%20This%20makes%20it%20harder%20for%20blood%20to%20flow%20freely%20and%20increases%20the%20chance%20of%20cholesterol%20and%20fat%20sticking%20to%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20arteries.%20Over%20time%2C%20this%20build-up%20%E2%80%94%20called%20plaque%20%E2%80%94%20can%20block%20the%20flow%20of%20blood%20to%20the%20heart%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20heart%20attack.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20who%20smoke%20have%20almost%20three%20to%20four%20times%20higher%20chances%20of%20having%20a%20heart%20attack%20compared%20to%20non-smokers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20role%20of%20diabetes%20and%20obesity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20diabetes%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20its%20prevalence%20among%20younger%20people%20is%20rising.%20Dr%20Rao%20warns%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20now%20see%20diabetes%20cases%20appearing%20at%20just%2030%20years%20of%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rao%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20with%20diabetes%20have%20a%20significantly%20higher%20risk%20of%20developing%20heart%20disease%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20due%20to%20shared%20risk%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20abnormal%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20and%20damage%20to%20blood%20vessels%20caused%20by%20high%20blood%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObesity%2C%20particularly%20metabolic%20syndrome%2C%20is%20another%20major%20contributor.%20Metabolic%20syndrome%20refers%20to%20a%20cluster%20of%20conditions%20that%20occur%20together%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20and%20diabetes.%20This%20condition%20is%20an%20umbrella%20term%20for%20high%20cholesterol%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20high%20blood%20sugar%2C%20and%20high%20body%20mass%20index%20(BMI).%20Dr%20Rao%20explains%2C%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20young%20people%20today%20have%20metabolic%20syndrome%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20more%20prone%20to%20heart%20attacks.%20Maintaining%20a%20BMI%20below%2024.5%20and%20reducing%20body%20weight%20by%205%25%20within%20three%20to%20six%20months%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20this%20risk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20lifestyle%20factors%20are%20crucial%2C%20genetics%20also%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20many%20cases%20of%20heart%20disease.%20High%20LDL%20(low-density%20lipoprotein)%20cholesterol%2C%20often%20above%20190%2C%20is%20sometimes%20linked%20to%20familial%20hypercholesterolemia%2C%20a%20genetic%20condition%20that%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20person%20has%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease%20before%2050%20years%20of%20age%20and%20has%20high%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20it%20may%20be%20genetic.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20aggressive%20management%20is%20required%20through%20medications%20or%20newer%20injectable%20treatments%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20not%20ignore%20these%20symptoms%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20in%20diagnosing%20heart%20attacks%20in%20young%20people%20is%20the%20variation%20in%20symptoms.%20Traditional%20signs%20like%20chest%20pain%20are%20not%20always%20present.%20Dr%20Rao%20highlights%20some%20of%20the%20most%20common%20indicators%3A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20mistake%20prolonged%20chest%20pain%20for%20gastric%20issues.%20If%20pain%20lasts%20more%20than%2010%20minutes%20and%20is%20associated%20with%20sweating%2C%20jaw%20pain%2C%20or%20left-hand%20pain%2C%20it%20should%20be%20taken%20seriously%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T151844.373-1744019410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20person%20with%20hand%20pain%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T151844.373-1744019410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T151844.373-1744019410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T151844.373-1744019410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T151844.373-1744019410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T151844.373-1744019410-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418275%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20other%20symptoms%20like%20hand%20pain%2C%20jaw%20pain%20etc.%20Picture%20source%3A%20Canva.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20may%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367755%2Fworld-heart-day-heart-disease-heart-attack-women-symptoms-warning-signs-cardiologists%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20different%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9C50%25%20of%20females%20do%20not%20experience%20chest%20pain.%20Instead%2C%20they%20may%20have%20hand%20pain%2C%20jaw%20pain%2C%20excessive%20sweating%2C%20giddiness%2C%20fatigue%2C%20or%20breathlessness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20we%20prevent%20this%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventing%20heart%20disease%20begins%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffirst-aid-for-heart-attack-part-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20routine%20health%20monitoring%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dr%20Rao%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20one%20should%20check%20blood%20pressure%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year.%20The%20target%20should%20be%20a%20systolic%20pressure%20below%20130%20and%20a%20diastolic%20pressure%20below%2080.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20keeping%20cholesterol%20levels%20in%20check%20is%20crucial.%20%E2%80%9CA%20total%20cholesterol%20level%20should%20be%20below%20200%2C%20and%20LDL%20should%20always%20be%20less%20than%20100%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20healthy%20sugar%20levels%20also%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%3A%20An%20LDL%20below%20100%2C%20a%20three-month%20average%20sugar%20level%20below%205.7%2C%20and%20a%20fasting%20blood%20sugar%20level%20below%20100%20is%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rao%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418283%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20essential%20to%20have%20a%20heart%20check-up%20every%20year%20post%2018%20years.%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth-e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2Fwhat-are-the-benefits-of-regular-heart-check-ups.webp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHealth-e%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20day-to-day%20level%2C%20these%20lifestyle%20changes%20can%20help%20prevent%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311579%2Fcardiologist-dr-deepak-krishnamurthy-breaks-myth-heart-attack-pain-relief-viral-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20cardiac%20diseases%20effectively%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExercise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Walking%2010%2C000%20steps%20per%20day%20significantly%20reduces%20cardiovascular%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Avoid%20red%20meat%2C%20which%20is%20high%20in%20saturated%20fats%2C%20and%20instead%20consume%20polyunsaturated%20fatty%20acids%20found%20in%20sunflower%20and%20olive%20oil.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStress%20management%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yoga%20and%20meditation%20can%20help%20control%20stress%2C%20which%20is%20a%20silent%20contributor%20to%20heart%20disease.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20all%20heart%20attacks%20result%20in%20cardiac%20arrest%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20confuse%20heart%20attacks%20with%20other%20cardiac%20conditions%20like%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrest%20or%20cardiomyopathy.%20Dr%20Rao%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20all%20cases%20of%20sudden%20collapse%20in%20the%20gym%20are%20due%20to%20heart%20attacks.%20There%20are%20other%20conditions%20like%20hypertrophic%20cardiomyopathy%20or%20ventricular%20arrhythmias%20that%20can%20cause%20sudden%20cardiac%20death.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20engaging%20in%20high-intensity%20workouts%2C%20he%20advises%20a%20thorough%20heart%20check-up.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20above%2040%2C%20or%20those%20with%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20diabetes%2C%20or%20hypertension%2C%20should%20undergo%20tests%20like%20ECG%20or%20treadmill%20tests%20before%20engaging%20in%20strenuous%20exercise.%E2%80%9D%20These%20tests%20help%20detect%20abnormalities%20in%20heart%20rhythm%2C%20blood%20flow%2C%20or%20stress-related%20changes%20that%20may%20signal%20underlying%20heart%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20heart%20disease%20among%20young%20Indians%20is%20a%20pressing%20concern.%20While%20some%20factors%20like%20genetics%20cannot%20be%20controlled%2C%20lifestyle%20modifications%2C%20early%20detection%2C%20and%20routine%20monitoring%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20risks.%20As%20Dr%20Rao%20stresses%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20important%20step%20is%20primary%20prevention%20%E2%80%94%20preventing%20the%20disease%20before%20it%20occurs%20by%20maintaining%20optimal%20health%20markers%20and%20avoiding%20known%20risk%20factors%20like%20smoking%20and%20physical%20inactivity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20increasing%20awareness%2C%20proactive%20healthcare%2C%20and%20lifestyle%20changes%2C%20the%20alarming%20rise%20in%20heart%20attacks%20among%20young%20Indians%20can%20be%20curtailed%2C%20ensuring%20a%20healthier%20future%20for%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fxplore%2F2025%2FFeb%2F24%2F50-of-heart-attack-cases-since-2020-among-adults-below-40%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E50%25%20of%20heart%20attack%20cases%20since%202020%20among%20adults%20below%2040%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20The%20New%20Ind